Changelog
=========

v0.2.12 (2014-11-28)
--------------------

- Add support for vagrant development. [tanelih]

- Fix invalid error message with duplicate user creation. [tanelih]

v0.2.11 (2014-11-26)
--------------------

- Add documentation for 'utils/error'. [tanelih]

v0.2.4 (2014-11-26)
-------------------

- Fix issue with 'passport' not propagating errors. [tanelih]

- Fix issue with 'gulp.watch' tracking too many files. Damn you
  'node_modules'... [tanelih]

v0.2.1 (2014-11-18)
-------------------

- Fix issue with request body size being set too low. [tanelih]

v0.2.0 (2014-11-18)
